title: Ep. #96 | Catching Up: Tablo of Epik High
description:
'Epik High is Here' and so is Tablo! Join the legendary hip-hop artist for an inside look at Epik High's long-awaited 10th studio album. Also on the podcast, Tablo reflects on 17 years with the group and spills the tea on fellow member and "driving force" Tukutz.

Eric wants to hear from YOU! Fill out this survey and join Eric in creating something special for the 100th episode of Kpop Daebak: https://bit.ly/3p2Eona
